{"tid":1598732,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"狗隻「捕捉、絕育、放回」計劃","createTime":"2019-09-27T15:28:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-27T15:28:32.000Z","uid":227748,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c29ad2321646ad476188c69a4ffc0063057bab51","tid":1598732,"uid":227748,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T15:28:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.spca.org.hk/ch/animal-birth-control/tnr-trap-neuter-return/tnr-trial-for-dogs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.spca.org.hk%2Fch%2Fanimal-birth-control%2Ftnr-trap-neuter-return%2Ftnr-trial-for-dogs&d=MLRnjlmMEh1el5UvTt2rHQKEBJewdHKi9Ib5gSSGE6s%3D&h=aea792f0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.spca.org.hk/ch/animal-birth-control/tnr-trap-neuter-return/tnr-trial-for-dogs</a><br />\n<br />\n作為一個狗主，真係好驚d流浪狗搞我隻狗女，近排聽朋友講佢d狗女比流浪狗搞，仲要幾隻一隻接一隻輪流搞佢隻狗女，狗女唔識講野，有冤無路訴，如果愛護動物協會真係推動到「捕捉，絕育，放回」就好啦！有無狗主認同？"}]}